<div id="about-title" class="title is-4 secondary-t center">Discover</div>
<div id="about-body-1" class="mt-2">
The  goal of Mokkalog is to have clothing from all over the world & be inclusive to all styles of clothing.
<br/>
Because we have so many variety, some clothing might not be for you. We are constantly striving to improve our design so it is easy for you to browse from a selection you enjoy.
</div>

<div class="mt-2">
<span id="bold3"class="bold">Open Platform:</span>
<span id="about-body-3">
Mokkalog is an <span class="bold">open listing platform</span> meaning The clothing that are uploaded by the people are not associated with Mokkalog. <span class="bold">Please becareful when browsing brands that are not verified.</span>
</span>
</div>

